questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;Read the give statements and conclusions carefully. Decide which of the given conclusion(s) follow(s) based on the given statements.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Statement:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;M&amp;nbsp;&amp;le; N &amp;lt; O, A&amp;nbsp;&amp;ge; B &amp;lt; C = O&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conclusions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I. N &amp;gt; B&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;II. C &amp;gt; M&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given: &lt;/strong&gt;M&amp;nbsp;&amp;le; N &amp;lt; O, A&amp;nbsp;&amp;ge; B &amp;lt; C = O&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The combined inequality can be represented as:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;A &amp;ge; B &amp;lt; C = O&amp;nbsp;&amp;gt; N&amp;nbsp;&amp;ge; M&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Explanation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I. N &amp;gt; B &amp;rarr; False ( as N &amp;lt; O = C &amp;gt; B &amp;rarr; a definite relation between N&amp;nbsp;and B cannot be determined))&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;II. C &amp;gt; M &amp;rarr; True ( as C = O &amp;gt; N &amp;ge; M is defined&amp;nbsp; relation between C and M)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;Only conclusion II follows&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

questions.statement:
Select the set in which the numbers are related in the same way as are the numbers of the following sets.&lt;br /&gt;
(NOTE: Operations should be performed on the whole numbers, without breaking down the numbers into its constituent digits. E.g. 13 &amp;ndash; Operations on 13 such as adding/deleting/multiplying etc. to 13 can be performed. Breaking down 13 into 1 and 3 and then performing mathematical operations on 1 and 3 is not allowed)&lt;br /&gt;
(9, 63, 7)&lt;br /&gt;
(27, 189, 21)

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;(9, 63, 7)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;63&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; 9 = 7&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;63&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; 7 = 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;And,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;(27, 189, 21)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;189 &amp;divide; 27 = 7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;189 &amp;divide; 21 = 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, checking each option one by one:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;(45, 315, 35)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;315 &amp;divide; 45&amp;nbsp;= 7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;315 &amp;divide; 35 = 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;(45, 315, 33)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;315 &amp;divide; 45&amp;nbsp;= 7&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;315 &amp;divide; 33 = 9.54&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;&amp;ne; 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 3)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;(45, 310, 35)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;310 &amp;divide; 45&amp;nbsp;= 6.88&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;&amp;ne; 7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;310 &amp;divide; 35 = &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 4)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;(40, 315, 35)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;315 &amp;divide; 40&amp;nbsp;= 7.87&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;&amp;ne; 7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;315 &amp;divide; 35 = &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Thus, out of all the options, &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;(45, 315, 35)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; follows the same logic as given.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 1&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-binding&quot; ng-bind-html=&quot;getSol(questionsExtraInfoDetails.q, &#039;en&#039;)&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage437.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 101px; width: 470px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-binding&quot; ng-bind-html=&quot;getSol(questionsExtraInfoDetails.q, &#039;en&#039;)&quot;&gt;The logic follows&amp;nbsp;here is:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/03/F1_Madhuri_Teaching_16.03.2023_D15.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 109px; height: 351px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Thus, the missing term is &amp;#39;TD&amp;#39;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;TD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After arranging the jumbled words given in options:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;USTOL&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; LOTUS&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;PLEPANEPI&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; PINEAPPLE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;ROWELSFUN&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; SUNFLOWER&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;NIMESAJ&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; JASMINE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Except Pineapple, all are flowers. So, Pineapple is odd one.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Option 2&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The code for each word is shown below:&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/10/F2_Savita_SSC_12-10-22_D6.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 336px; height: 111px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Clearly,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;cricket&amp;#39; be&amp;nbsp;written as &amp;#39;mo&amp;#39; in that language.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;mo&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39; is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;

