questions.statement:
&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Refer to the following number series and answer the question.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;7 2 9 6 3 7 3 9 7 7 3 9 7 3 2 2 1 3 3 9 3 7 3 9 3 9&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;How many 3s are there that are immediately preceded by 7 and immediately followed by 9?&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;We have to find the triad which looks like (7,3,9) in the given series:&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/02/F1_Railway_Amit%20A_19-02-2023_D21.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 569px; height: 42px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We can see that there are 3 such triads where 3 is i&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;mmediately preceded by 7 and immediately followed by 9.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;b&gt;&amp;quot; Three &amp;quot;.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Given:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Seven sisters, Anita, Babita, Sunita, Dixita, Rita, Lalita and Geeta are standing in a row facing north.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;Lalita is standing to the immediate right of Rita who stands fourth to the right of Geeta.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Case 1:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/02/F1_Madhuri_SSC_03.02.2023_D62.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 432px; height: 112px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Case 2:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

