&lt;p&gt;2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Dixita stands at the middle position.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;Case 1:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

