&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;Mukesh stands in the 4th position from the front in a queue and there are 2 persons between Mukesh and Rakesh.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2) &lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Rakesh stands after Mukesh.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

