&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3)&amp;nbsp;The first person is removed from the queue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Here,&amp;nbsp;after removing the first person, the queue&amp;#39;s positions shift forward i.e.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;New position from front = (Original position - 1 person removed from front)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Mukesh&amp;#39;s new position = (4 - 1)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 3rd&amp;nbsp;from front&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Rakesh&amp;#39;s new position = (7 - 1)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 6th from front&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage674daac8bd8ee75d3e74900a.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Thus, the&amp;nbsp;position of Rakesh from the front of the queue is &amp;#39;6th&amp;#39;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 2&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;
